{"tid":2479030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(多圖）加油站正妹自拍照爆紅　「制服底下辣翻」老闆下令：不准","createTime":"2021-04-07T13:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T13:45:09.000Z","uid":380132,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ca24d72fc682ff31fd7298804fd96c5fbebcbd61","tid":2479030,"uid":380132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T13:35:10.000Z","msg":"國際中心／賴俊佑報導<br />\n<br />\n香港一名在加油站工作的長髮正妹Emilyck Chan，因為一張在加油站自拍的照片，在各大臉書社團爆紅，更有網友造訪她的臉書發現，原來Emilyck Chan非常火辣，搞到加油站老闆都知道，下令她不准在加油站拍照。<br />\n<br />\nEmilyck Chan經常在臉書、IG分享性感照片，但真正讓她爆紅的，卻是一張在加油站自拍的照片，而網友造訪她的臉書，才發現制服底下的身材原來這麼火辣，驚呼「請問加油站在哪裡？我要去加油」、「這間加油站專請美女？」、「好想去加油」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmckkh7TCssyXmyDiYKNubb1B2bhbBhdMioaqPJ2e7rRNw?filename=awCnbFO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FawCnbFO.jpg&h=4e9306e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而Emilyck Chan在各大臉書瘋傳，就連加油站老闆都知道，下令她不准在加油站拍照，事後Emilyck Chan發文表示，還好工作有保住，要大家不要擔心。<br />\n<br />\n不過Emilyck Chan爆紅後，湧入大量私人訊息，有網友懷疑是不是女模特扮加油站工讀生製造話題，更有網友調侃身材條件這麼好「怎不試看看別的工作」，對此，Emilyck Chan回應自己真的只是加油站工作人員，當時只想記錄工作當下，沒想到會爆紅，至於有網友好奇她在哪家加油站工作，Emilyck Chan表示不會說自己在哪上班，以免造成困擾。"},{"pid":"deef57db049d2089fe3b89e5f0efe75e1da48e1f","tid":2479030,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T13:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ab1819e534acabb481642704080d6c98e2f3c6","tid":2479030,"uid":159236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"多圖=一張圖"},{"pid":"69dfc9b74dd907024a5ee8f26e662613bc213710","tid":2479030,"uid":276865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T13:41:26.000Z","msg":"識唔識咩叫做多圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60be982655ad3b0e15d36923b52d753c956a1367","tid":2479030,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T13:41:36.000Z","msg":"救樓主老母<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://jdailyhk.com/2021/04/emilyck-chan/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjdailyhk.com%2F2021%2F04%2Femilyck-chan%2F&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=672a8c71\" target=\"_blank\">https://jdailyhk.com/2021/04/emilyck-chan/</a>"},{"pid":"d7acbadfde4706bfc04a67f291775d71a3bf7ee9","tid":2479030,"uid":345459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T13:42:00.000Z","msg":"嘩, 一禁入去就有3點睇<br />\n唔講得笑"},{"pid":"95b5f653aa9ee83182eab2ec60b00d96761b9b70","tid":2479030,"uid":33059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T13:43:34.000Z","msg":"又幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6f294ce4543d0e8c797b5e0e27d560003b8f02","tid":2479030,"uid":59538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T13:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625bca0d80bcb9c775ef9007238d53a6b9db9bef","tid":2479030,"uid":387907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T13:45:09.000Z","msg":"嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜我無車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唯有等viutv送一架畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}